{"tid":2184093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍偵察機行蹤異常　疑似直接從台灣起飛","createTime":"2020-09-01T10:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T11:33:44.000Z","uid":261647,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"70c6e9666f67fc43408278d0d5628fb827733933","tid":2184093,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200831/s00004/9c6c0945f13070bdeaea8c7a395937de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200831%2Fs00004%2F9c6c0945f13070bdeaea8c7a395937de.jpg&h=5071976e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - （「南海戰略態勢感知計劃」平台Twitter圖片）<br />\n<br />\n美國軍機近期在台灣附近動作頻頻，據「南海戰略態勢感知計劃」平台發布消息，一架美國海軍EP-3E電子偵察機（AE1D91）昨日（30日）出現在台灣以北近空，後經由東海前往日本，軌迹較為異常。這架EP-3E於29日曾前往台灣南海南部偵察，之後便沒有收到其來自沖繩嘉手納空軍基地的起降信號，疑似直接從台灣起飛。<br />\n<br />\n「南海戰略態勢感知計劃」平台表示，美國軍機詭異的飛行軌跡，不排除信號錯誤導致軌迹偏差的情況。目前暫未看到台灣方面對此事的回<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20200831/s00004/1598849055172/美軍偵察機行蹤異常-疑似直接從台灣起飛\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20200831%2Fs00004%2F1598849055172%2F%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E5%81%B5%E5%AF%9F%E6%A9%9F%E8%A1%8C%E8%B9%A4%E7%95%B0%E5%B8%B8-%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%9E%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E8%B5%B7%E9%A3%9B&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=b21647ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20200831%2Fs00004%2F1598849055172%2F%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E5%81%B5%E5%AF%9F%E6%A9%9F%E8%A1%8C%E8%B9%A4%E7%95%B0%E5%B8%B8-%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%9E%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E8%B5%B7%E9%A3%9B&h=af34a989\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20200831/s00004/1598849055172/美軍偵察機行蹤異常-疑似直接從台灣起飛</a>"},{"pid":"8a26beb84d11dc4fceab88995d3f948a0f4f160c","tid":2184093,"uid":143343,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:3